    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Paint based on a polyvinyl acetate medium. Diluted with water, but waterproof when dry, vinyl paint is highly opaque and is characterized by a matte finish.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
